-- Yemeni Army Kills 67 Militants in Fighting in South, Saba Says
-- B y   M o h a m m e d   H a t e m
-- 2012-05-24T13:33:52Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-24/yemeni-army-kills-35-militants-in-fighting-in-southern-province.html
Yemeni soldiers killed 67 militants
in fighting today in the southern province of Abyan, the state-
run Saba news agency reported in a text message.  The army on May 12 began a major attack against militants
in an effort to recapture cities that they hold.  To contact the reporter on this story:
